{"tid":2084373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國強硬反擊：對涉港問題上表現惡劣美方人員實施簽證限制","createTime":"2020-06-29T08:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T10:08:39.000Z","uid":7542,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"73e9e7979e20c5daed23309e62bfa1e927fa1af1","tid":2084373,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:06:19.000Z","msg":"中方決定對在涉及香港問題上表現惡劣的美方人員，實施簽證限制。外交部在例行記者會，回應日前美方宣布對中方有關涉港官員等實施簽證限制，發言人趙立堅表示，香港國家安全立法問題純屬中國內政，任何外國無權干涉。中國政府維護國家主權、安全、發展利益的決心堅定不移，貫徹「一國兩制」方針的決心堅定不移，反對任何外部勢力干涉香港事務的決心堅定不移。美方通過所謂制裁，阻撓中方推進香港國家安全立法的圖謀絕不會得逞。趙立堅說，針對美方有關錯誤行徑，中方決定，對在涉港問題上表現惡劣的美方人員實施簽證限制。"},{"pid":"24868266b8379fd49db050e9c116f581e7efe549","tid":2084373,"uid":69125,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:07:04.000Z","msg":"人唔笑警犬都吠"},{"pid":"fda0c9f13811c1d22c35534ed960a38be9e2cb44","tid":2084373,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:07:15.000Z","msg":"Source: <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534689-20200629.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534689-20200629.htm&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=72dd6cad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534689-20200629.htm&h=fea2ad23\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534689-20200629.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi7ZF_dgqG3s&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=97e002fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s</a>"},{"pid":"be24239d8591bd5bf3f4c8deb02b2255bc66aaa1","tid":2084373,"uid":7542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"24868266b8379fd49db050e9c116f581e7efe549","tid":2084373,"uid":69125,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:07:04.00